column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
As a doctor, my job is to help diagnose illnesses and provide treatment advice. I am here to help with any questions you have about your health.
Unfortunately, I am not available 24/7. However, if you experience any significant changes in your symptoms, I encourage you to contact a local physician or emergency services.
so what can you do for me

I can help you diagnose any issues you may be having and recommend treatment options based on your symptoms. I also can provide information on preventive health measures so that you can take care of yourself and stay healthy.
Is there something specific you'd like to know about?
Are you experiencing any medical symptoms or changes in your health? It would be helpful to better understand if I can help you with anything.
no i'm fine at present thank
That's great to hear! I'm glad you're feeling well. Please don't hesitate to reach out if you have any other medical questions.
I'm sorry, I don't understand. Could you please rephrase the question in English?
